# UI rules

- Use shadcn/ui components; mobile-first (test at 375px)
- SSE report streaming: skeleton placeholders to avoid layout shift
- Do not import `lib/store`, `@vercel/kv`, or server-only modules in client components
- Public report pages at `/runs/[id]` read from API/KV via server components or fetch
